_sText:
Dm_devcorners
This is my second map, my first being dm_devarena.  This map started as a simple Idea; the four different quadrants of the map would represent four different climate zones, but than I realized, I sucked with displacements.  It was as simple as that, so I put the .vmf aside and went on with my life,  Than I decided to make a new map, dm_devarena,  after completing this map I wanted more and I had remembered that I had a 35% done map just lying in my folders. So I Opened it and began working on it.  I also had optimized many things, I made several pieces of architecture a func_detail to lower compile times, I kept a skybox to a little 2x8 piece in the ceiling at the center.  I also used NoDraw on many of the textures that went unseen, you know the usual mapping stuff.


-This Map Is Completly  Symmetrical (not completly :\ )
-Features many areas for cover and to ambush
-Heavily tested with a team of me and 19 bots
-Supports 20 People
-Not too heavy for snipers with the exception of the outer linings.  
-Probably Best with a shotgun or M4/AK 

*Quick Note* If someone runs a dedicated server and want's to use the map, just give me a quick heads up
